---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Our Story | RIPPLE Bakes & Makes" description="The story behind RIPPLE Bakes & Makes, where handmade meets homemade."><section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><span class="eyebrow">Our story</span><h1 class="display">A home for the things<br/>made with <em>heart.</em></h1><p>RIPPLE Bakes &amp; Makes began with a simple belief: the things we make and share should feel personal.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container about-story"><div class="image-panel image-panel--rose"><span class="image-label">From our hands to yours</span></div><div><span class="eyebrow">The idea</span><h2 class="display">Two creative loves,<br/>woven <em>together.</em></h2><p>There’s something quietly special about a fresh loaf on the counter, a handmade gift wrapped for someone you love, or a familiar fabric made useful again. RIPPLE is a gathering place for those kinds of moments.</p><p>We bring baking and handmade arts together under one warm, detail-loving roof — creating small-batch treats and custom pieces that are made to be enjoyed, used, and remembered.</p></div></div></section><section class="section section--paper"><div class="container values"><article><span>01</span><h2>Care in the details</h2><p>We slow down where it matters, giving every order the attention it deserves.</p></article><article><span>02</span><h2>Beauty in the useful</h2><p>We love things that bring joy and earn their place in everyday life.</p></article><article><span>03</span><h2>Made for connection</h2><p>From a shared cookie to a personal gift, our favourite work brings people closer.</p></article></div></section></MainLayout>
<style>.about-story{align-items:center;display:grid;gap:7rem;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.about-story .image-panel{height:460px}.about-story p{color:var(--muted)}.values{display:grid;gap:2rem;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.values article{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:1rem}.values span{color:var(--sage);font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600}.values h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:500;margin:.7rem 0}.values p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem}@media(max-width:750px){.about-story{gap:3rem;grid-template-columns:1fr}.about-story .image-panel{height:350px}.values{grid-template-columns:1fr}}</style>
